sub_title: Research Analyst and Hog commercial manager at The Twins Group
summary:
•	Work ethic: Able to capture key part of work and focus on priority. Deliver results under high pressure and time limitation. 
•	Quantitative background: Sophisticated programming skill, implementation of statistical analysis and the ability to process large amount of data. 
•	Diversified knowledge: Understand fundamental analysis, database, physical commodity market and derivatives.
